  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "The IP65 rated FUZE PAR Z120 IP™ is a single source par luminaire with a 120W Quad Color RGBW COB LED. Features 7° to 55° motorized zoom, RGBW color mixing, electronic strobe and selectable dimming curve effects, DMX and RDM (remote device management) protocol support, IP rated 5pin XLR and IP65 Locking Power Cable in/out connections, LCD menu display with 4 touch button control panel, dual adjustable yokes, multiple unit power linking, flicker free operation for TV and FILM, a multi-voltage universal auto switching power supply (110-240v), and removable gel frame and barn doors included.",
